Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得她太可爰 就看入神了
